Description:
The room is full of empty chests, and there is a door that divides the vault. 

The keyhole of the door has been sabotaged, and you’re sure the pirates have hidden something interesting on the other side. 

There are some nice paintings showing a captain with a white beard at different moments in his life. Your adventurer senses are tingling. You have a feeling that there must be a trap, but you can’t see it.
